snippet.title: Amber Heard's Former Assistant Exposes Her
snippet.description:
Amber Heard's Former Assistant Exposes Her.

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
_____________________________________________

Johnny Depp and Amber Heard’s legal teams are collecting statements and testimony from those who comprised the inner circle around the couple during their marriage, and now Amber’s former assistant has gone on record that she was mentally and verbally abused by Her.
Let’s find out what she has to say about Amber Heard. 

_____________________________________________
